<HEADLINE> News Items from Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 15 (Xinhua) -- Following are news items from
the Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua in Hong Kong today:

hke081533 -- National Mourning Day Observed in Bangladesh
hka081534 -- Hong Kong Releases Domestic Export Figures
hka081535 -- Hang Seng China Enterprises Index Down
hka081536 -- Gold Price in Hong Kong Down
hke081537 -- 11 Still Missing in Philippine Ship Capsize
hka081538 -- HKSAR Official On Legislative Council Bill
