<HEADLINE> Indonesia Hopes Cambodia to Join ASEAN This Year </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, August 16 (Xinhua) -- President Soeharto today said
Indonesia hoped Cambodia could join the Association of Southeast
Asian Nations (ASEAN) this year.
</P>
<P>
In his address to parliament in commemoration of the 52nd
anniversary of the country's independence, Soeharto said
Indonesia, along with other members of the association, is ready
to help Cambodia solve its problem.
</P>
<P>
