other countries, Indonesia together with other ASEAN member
countries stand ready to help if it is requested by the
conflicting parties in that country," he said.
</P>
<P>
Cambodia's membership in the association, scheduled to be
accepted together with that of Laos and Myanmar last month, has
been postponed indefinitely following the political crisis in that
country marked by the ousting of first prime minister Ranariddh.
</P>
