</P>
<P>
The inscription for the hall was written by Jiang Zemin,
General Secretary of the CPC Central Committee.
</P>
<P>
Hu Jintao, a member of the Standing Committee of the Political
Bureau of the CPC Central Committee and of the Secretariat of the
Central Committee, extended congratulations to the opening of the
hall on behalf of the Party Central Committee and extended regards
to Li Dazhao's relatives.
</P>
