the banner of Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with
Chinese characteristics and rally closely around the Party Central
Committee with Jiang Zemin at the core."
</P>
<P>
The hall is built on 6.6 hectares of land and is listed as one
of China's 100 patriotism education bases. The hall's 500 photos
and historical relics give a picture of Li's life and experiences.
</P>
<P>
Li Peng, Qiao Shi, Li Ruihuan, Liu Huaqing, and other Chinese
senior officials also wrote inscriptions for the hall. 
