activities of its navy personnel.
</P>
<P>
The CN-235 is a multi-purpose, dual engine aircraft jointly
produced with Casa of Spain.
</P>
<P>
The aircraft has a speed of up to 250 nautical miles per hour,
can carry 35 passengers and can be used for both commercial and
military purpose.  
