project for building the Second Power Plant in Shentou, Shanxi
Province.
</P>
<P>
China is going to negotiate with the Czech side over a range of
issues including the equipment import and loans for two complete
sets of 500,000-kilowatt power generators, Shi added.
</P>
<P>
